alert.note: Alert for East Sweetwater County (Wyoming) Issued by the National Weather Service

info.headline: High Wind Warning issued December 14 at 11:40AM MST until December 14 at 8:00PM MST by NWS Riverton
info.description: ...HIGH WIND WARNING REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 PM MST THIS EVENING... * WHAT...South winds 30 to 40 mph with gusts up to 65 mph. * WHERE...East Sweetwater County. * WHEN...Until 8 PM MST this evening. * IMPACTS...Damaging winds are possible. Travel could be difficult, especially for high profile vehicles. This will be a strong crosswind across Interstate 80. * ADDITIONAL DETAILS...South winds with gusts of 50 to 55 mph, with an isolated gust up to 60 mph, will remain possible tonight.
info.instruction: Monitor the latest forecasts and warnings for updates on this situation. Use caution if you must drive. In a parking lot, park into the wind to minimize the possibility of your car door hitting another parked vehicle.
